<title>USA: Famous Dave's names new executives.</title>
<headline>Famous Dave's names new executives.</headline>
<dateline>MINNEAPOLIS 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Famous Dave's of America Inc said chief operating officer Douglas Lanham was named to the additional job of chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Dave Anderson will relinquish the CEO title and remain chairman, the company said.</p>
<p>Mark Payne, formerly chief financial officer, was named president.</p>
<p>Steven Opdahl was hired as the new chief financial officer. Opdahl was formerly an accountant at Honeywell, the company said.</p>
<p>Famous Dave's operates three Famous Dave's restaurants and has six more in development.</p>
<p>((--Chicago Newsdesk 312-408-8787))</p>
